service.name: ABSTUDY School Fees Allowance
service.description: ABSTUDY School Fees Allowance (SFA) assists students and their parent(s)/guardian(s) to meet the costs of school fees levied by the approved education institution. Home schooled and distance education students also qualify for SFA even though they do not physically attend at a school, as they may have fees levied by the education institution which meet SFA requirements.
